Package: HILAMA
Type: Package
Title: HILAMA: High-dimensional exposure mediation analysis with latent confounder
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Xinbo Wang
Maintainer: Xinbo Wang <cinbo_w@sjtu.edu.cn>
Description: A high dimensional mediation method to identify the nonzero acitive paths from high dimensional exposures, high dimensional mediators and continous outcome, that can provide a guarantee of false discovery rate control in finite sample settings.
